  =======================================================
  WIDE AWAKE COFFEE - ADMIN TAGGING SYSTEM GUIDE
  =======================================================
  
  This theme uses a flexible tag-based system for categorizing coffee products.
  Admins can easily tag products in Shopify Admin to control filtering and display.
  
  HOW TO TAG PRODUCTS:
  ===================
  
  1. Go to Shopify Admin ‚Üí Products
  2. Select a product to edit
  3. In the "Tags" field, add the appropriate tags
  4. Save the product
  
  COFFEE VIBE TAGS:
  ================
  These control the flavor badge displayed on product cards and filtering:
  
  üçØ Smooth and Sweet:
