  FLEXIBLE FORMAT:
  ===============
  You can use either format:
  - Direct tags: smooth-sweet, daily-driver
  - Prefixed tags: vibe:smooth-sweet, segment:daily-driver
  
  DEFAULTS:
  =========
  If no tags are added:
  - Vibe: smooth-sweet (üçØ Smooth and Sweet)
  - Segment: daily-driver (‚òï Daily Driver)
  
  TIPS:
  =====
  - Tags are case-insensitive (Smooth-Sweet = smooth-sweet)
